   We do not serve as a referral agency for various alternative medical
   treatments or individual practitioners. The NCCAM facilitates and
   conducts biomedical research.

   Do not seek the therapies described on these pages without consulting a
   licensed health care provider. Inclusion of a treatment or resource on
   the NCCAM Web site does not imply endorsement by the NCCAM, the NIH, or
   the Department of Health and Human Services (DHHS).

